      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-04-22T16:46:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Some temperatures are reported in non-Celsius.\n\nSwarming does some guesses to convert them:\nhttps://github.com/luci/luci-py/blob/e0a8a5640c4104e5c90781d833168aa8a8d1f24d/appengine/third_party/python-adb/adb/contrib/high.py#L649\nhttps://chrome-internal.googlesource.com/infradata/config/+/refs/heads/master/configs/chromium-swarm/scripts/skia_mobile.py#748\n\nShould we emulate this?",
      "range": {
